---
import ShopLayout from '~/layouts/ShopLayout.astro';
---

<ShopLayout
  title="Accessibility statement – PURIST"
  description="Our commitment to making PURIST accessible to everyone."
>
  <section class="container-x py-16 lg:py-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Accessibility statement</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-tight tracking-tight mb-8 text-balance">
      Built to be used by <em class="font-medium">everyone.</em>
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-brand-gray-900/90 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        PURIST is committed to making this site usable for people of all abilities. We
        design and develop against the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1
        at Level AA as our minimum standard.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-10 mb-4">What we do</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li>Semantic HTML with a logical heading hierarchy on every page.</li>
        <li>Sufficient colour contrast for body text and interactive elements.</li>
        <li>Visible focus indicators for keyboard navigation.</li>
        <li>ARIA labels on icon-only controls and a skip-to-content link at the top of each page.</li>
        <li>Respect for the operating system's <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code> preference.</li>
        <li>Form labels associated with their inputs; required fields marked accordingly.</li>
        <li>Image alt text describing meaningful visual content; decorative images marked as such.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-10 mb-4">What we are still working on</h2>
      <p class="text-sm">
        Accessibility is an ongoing practice, not a finished state. If you encounter a
        barrier on this site, we want to hear about it. Email
        <a href="mailto:accessibility@purist.online" class="underline underline-offset-4">accessibility@purist.online</a>
        with a description of the issue and the page where you saw it. We commit to
        responding within five business days.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-10 mb-4">Third-party content</h2>
      <p class="text-sm">
        Where this site embeds content from third parties (video, social feeds, payment
        processors), we ask those providers to meet the same accessibility standards.
        We cannot guarantee third-party accessibility but we will work with you to find
        an alternative way to access the same information on request.
      </p>

      <p class="text-xs text-brand-gray-600 mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-brand-gray-200">
        Last reviewed: May 2026. We review this statement at least annually.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</ShopLayout>
